OL,5, Referrals to bailiffs in England and   
OL,6, Wales to recover unpaid council debts  
OL,7, have risen by nearly 20%, a BBC        
OL,8, investigation has found.               
OL,10,FBirmingham's 500% rise in referrals    
OL,11,Fbetween 2022 and 2023 topped the list  
OL,12,Fof 280 councils that replied to a File 
OL,13,Fon 4 Freedom of Information request.   
OL,15,FFigures suggest there is #500m of      
OL,16,Funcollected public debt each year,     
OL,17,Fadding to councils' strained finances. 
OL,19,FOne bailiff said he was incentivised to
OL,20,Fuse underhand tactics.                 
